data.description: Welcome home! This stunning property boasts a charming exterior and is nestled within a well-kept subdivision. Step onto the huge 28ft long front porch and envision yourself relaxing on warm summer evenings. As you enter, you'll be captivated by the spaciousness and style. The home offers three bedrooms and two bathrooms spread across 1,302 square feet, ensuring ample space for comfortable living. The cathedral ceilings create an open and airy atmosphere, while the gas fireplace adds warmth and coziness during the colder months. One of the features of this home is the floored attic, providing additional storage space. The HVAC system was recently cleaned out in 2021, ensuring optimal performance and energy efficiency. The roof was replaced in 2020 and comes with a transferable warranty, offering peace of mind for years to come. The updated closet systems provide convenient organization solutions, making it easy to keep your belongings in order. The owner has taken great care of this property, including the installation of a new water softener in 2019. The spacious back patio is perfect for outdoor entertaining or simply enjoying the tranquility of the surrounding neighborhood. Recent updates include brand new flooring (2021) and fresh paint throughout (2023), giving the home a modern and refreshed look. The washer and dryer, (new in 2021) will be staying with the property, making laundry a breeze. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this house your new home. Schedule a showing today and start creating lasting memories in this wonderful home!
